

- Task 1: Develop a class (QuizCLI) that manages the command line interface for
the user to complete different quizzes and perform other quiz related actions.

- Task 2: Develop a class (TBD) that will record and manage a history of
different quiz sessions that the user has taken over time.

- Task 3: Develop a class (TBD) that will keeps track of the user's responses in
a session, allowing the user to see explanations of their wrong answers.